modShortDescription: So, a few weeks ago, Roland was kind enough to send Guppycur a pic of himself and allowed Guppycur to use his real life likeness to make a zombie.
modDescription:
So, a few weeks ago, Roland was kind enough to send Guppycur a pic of himself and allowed Guppycur to use his real life likeness to make a [zombie](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-zombies/), and Guppycur completely thought it was in the [creature pack](https://7daystodiemods.com/creature-packs-a-community-entity-project/), but it is notâ€¦ Guppycur think he missed content lock deadline, so he present to you: Zombie Roland! This will work with creature pack, however you will need to add him to spawns yourself.

**[Download](https://gitlab.com/guppycur/guppymods/-/archive/master/guppymods-master.zip?path=Guppycur%27s_Roland_Zombie)**

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/9144-guppycurs-modlets/).

**Credits:** [Guppycur](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/guppycur/)
